## 10. Conventions & Patterns

- **All models and routes in `app.py`** тАФ no blueprints, no separate models package
- **Models = database schema** тАФ columns map directly to DB columns; schema changes = model changes
- **Dark theme throughout** тАФ `bg-dark text-light` body, `bg-secondary` cards
- **No custom CSS/JS files** тАФ all styling via Bootstrap utilities, all JS inline in templates
- **AJAX for inline edits** тАФ Notes and PixInsight workflow use fetch() + JSON endpoints
- **Forms use POST with redirect** тАФ standard PRG pattern for all non-AJAX forms
- **GlobalConfig DB model** тАФ primary config store (observer location, defaults); .env provides DB URL + secrets
- **DatabaseMigrator** тАФ `config/migration.py` handles full bidirectional SQLiteтЖФPostgreSQL data migration with validation and backup
- **TargetType + ObjectMapping** тАФ auto-classification system: catalog names map to target types which recommend palettes
- **Cascade deletes** тАФ Target deletion cascades to plans + sessions; TargetType cascades to ObjectMappings
- **Preset system** тАФ filters/palettes/wheels can be exported/imported as JSON preset files
